{"tid":1954110,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"蹄姐 你可不要再鳩噏","createTime":"2020-04-01T14:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T16:32:55.000Z","uid":70356,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"370b3fcf030db8bcecefaabbb7a4cc47be96d1b0","tid":1954110,"uid":70356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"蹄姐 你可否不要再鳩噏<br />\n蹄姐 你冇事別來鳩叫<br />\n自那公開你撐條垃圾<br />\n回魂又返照閃一下<br />\n盡快收聲 彈開<br />\n<br />\n閪面 就此擁着最愛一家<br />\n生活 就過份地藍絲化<br />\nFB    假使嬲數比CY多過<br />\n沒有需要　驚訝<br />\n<br />\n蹄姐很清楚撐po好似拜神<br />\n真的身份不過廢物<br />\n這愛國蹄盡快犧牲<br />\n被揼無負這一生<br />\n周街恥笑拒絕同情<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n劣改落花流水，小弟不才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725db6d641abbf8c17ea0e1d91c0064a2c77ba3a","tid":1954110,"uid":281039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"呢度變得藏頭詩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0a819a57b5ed3bb19890b84fef87aad24b12f0","tid":1954110,"uid":281039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"725db6d641abbf8c17ea0e1d91c0064a2c77ba3a","tid":1954110,"uid":281039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"呢度變得藏頭詩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"呢度邊忽藏頭詩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a011558e21e0e47d00cff6100eb7d16a47e3c6d8","tid":1954110,"uid":70356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0a819a57b5ed3bb19890b84fef87aa